features: Large Air Fryer Basket for Oven: This large capacity air fryer basket measures 15.4"*11.5", which is equivalent to 2-3 regular trays. Plenty of cooking space for a large family's gourmet needs! This airfryer accessory suitable for many types of air fryers such as LG, Breville, Emeril, Ninja, Frigidaire, Samsung, Cuisinart etc.

Nonstick & Easy to Clean: This nonstick oven air fryer basket and tray were made of high quality food grade 304 stainless steel, BPA free and FDA compliant; the air fryer tray for oven is safe to use at temperatures up to 450°F, warp resistant and non-deformable; the nonstick coating on the surface releases food easily, which makes cleanup a breeze and saves you a lot of valuable time!

Healthier by Less Fat and Calories: The air fryer pans for oven filtered out excess fat in Food Ingredients, which means you can enjoy your favorite fried foods without having to worry about adding calories and fat. So you can cook crispy, healthy fried foods with less oil, while retaining their original flavor and nutrition.

360° Circulation Heating: The air fryer pan is designed with an ultra-fine mesh basket that circulates heat 360° to ensure food is heated evenly, so you don't need to turn or rotate your food while it's cooking. Air circulation reduces the chance of food burning and provides a perfect golden brown surface every time you bake.

Multi-Purpose Baking Basket: The air fryer accessories meets all kitchen needs and can be used for both commercial and home use. Perfect for baking homemade pizzas, chicken nuggets, sandwiches, chips and more. Ideal for everyday cooking, family dinners, friends gatherings, holiday celebrations and more. We offer 24-hour friendly service and one-year warranty promise, if you have any problem with the bakeware sets, please contact us promptly and we will solve it for you at the first time!

HOW TO CARE FOR NONSTICK BAKEWARE Allow baking pan to cool before cleaning. Never immerse hot bakeware in cold water. While bakeware sets are dishwasher safe, hand washing using a liquid dishwashing detergent and a nonabrasive cleaning sponge will keep your bakeware looking better longer
